    <content type="html">&lt;p&gt;There's a new rule that I'd like to apply to my blog.  Every article must be five sentences or less. Compound sentences are no exception.  If I cannot summarize my thoughts into five sentences or less, it probably should not be said.&lt;/p&gt;
